p1, drop next st off needle to front of work, p2, pick up dropped st and knit it; p2, sl the next 2 purl sts, drop next st off needle to front of work, sl the same 2 purl sts back to left-hand needle, pick up dropped st and knit it, p3
p3, sl 1 wyib, p2, sl 1 wyib, p3
k3, sl 1 wyif, k2, sl 1 wyif, k3

p3, drop next st to front of work, sl the 2 purl sts, drop next st off needle to front; then holding the 2 purl sts on right-hand needle, pick up the first dropped st on left-hand needle, then sl the 2 purl sts back to left-hand needle; then pick up second dropped st and return it to left-hand needle; then k1, p2, k1 across these 4 sts, p3
